title: DeMartini's walk-off double lifts No. 5 Hokies past 'Cats - VT hokiesports.com
content: DeMartini's walk-off double lifts No. 5 Hokies past 'Cats  VT hokiesports.com
description: With rookie Carson DeMartini delivering the game-winning, ground-rule double during the bottom of the ninth inning on Sunday, the No. 5 Virginia Tech baseball team walked off Villanova, 3-2, to finish a two-game sweep of the Wildcats at English Field at Atlantic Union Bank Park.
